   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>[Month, day.] Isidoros, son of Ision(?), delivered through Palemon for the account of the villagers of Kainos, Karanis, for the sixteenth indiction two hundred forty pounds of chaff, that is, 240 lbs. (2nd hand) I, Ision, have signed.</ab>
